Package: gao
Type: Package
Title: A Complete Library of GAO Reports and Metadata
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person(c("Jack", "T."), "Rametta", email = "jtrametta@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9841-146X"))
Description: Download reports published by the United States Government
    Accountability Office (GAO) directly from <https://www.gao.gov>. Ships
    with a bundled dataset of over 55,000 report URLs spanning 1921 to the
    present. Provides a one-step download function that filters by fiscal
    year and format, and a text extraction utility for downloaded PDFs.
    Requires 'curl-impersonate' as a system dependency to handle TLS
    fingerprint filtering. Not affiliated with or endorsed by the
    U.S. Government Accountability Office.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    rvest
